NEW YORK, N. H. & H. R. CO. v. WEISBERG. (Circuit Court of Appeals, First Circuit. April 14, 1903.) No. 469. David S. Baker, for plaintiff in error. Lucius Brown, for defendant in error.

Before COLT and PUTNAM, Circuit Judges, and ALDRICH, District Judge.

No opinion. Dismissed by agreement of counsel.
